data.description: SELLER TO PAY UP TO $1500 IN BUYER INCENTIVE! Traditional home with front porch and back porch . Granite countertops, LVP flooring, with fresh paint throughout home. Open kitchen, dining Rm and living Rm. Man cave or den with an outside entrance/exit. Master bdrm on main floor and other 2 bedrooms on top floor. Laundry Rm and fenced back yard with outbuilding. Convenient to Macon, Robins AF Base and I75. Make an appointment now.
